<span id="freeTextContainer5575265700335498077">I cannot believe this took me so long to read. <br/><br/>In the spirit of A Little Princess, this story recognises the characteristics we must prize most as human beings. The book follows contrary Mary Lennox as she learns a very important lesson from a very secret garden.</span>

